=== RAW MODEL ANSWER ===
Answer: Step 1: N-methylate 4-iodo-1H-pyrazole (MeI, K2CO3) to give 4-iodo-1-methyl-1H-pyrazole. | Step 2: Suzuki couple 4-iodo-1-methyl-1H-pyrazole with 4-bromophenylboronic acid (Pd catalyst, base) to form 4-(4-bromophenyl)-1-methyl-1H-pyrazole, then Miyaura borylation (B2pin2, Pd) to the corresponding 4-(1-methyl-1H-pyrazol-4-yl)phenyl boronate ester. | Step 3: Suzuki couple that boronate with methyl 4-chloroquinazoline-6-carboxylate to give methyl 4-(4-(1-methyl-1H-pyrazol-4-yl)phenyl)quinazoline-6-carboxylate. | Step 4: Hydrolyze the methyl ester to 4-(4-(1-methyl-1H-pyrazol-4-yl)phenyl)quinazoline-6-carboxylic acid, then couple with 4-methoxybenzylamine (HATU or EDCI) to furnish COc1ccc(CNC(=O)c2ccc3cncc(-c4ccc(-c5cnn(C)c5)cc4)c3n2)cc1.

